# @node-versions: v26.1.0
# @description: Register smol_primordial native binding in NODE_BUILTIN_BINDINGS
#
# Adds V(smol_primordial) alongside the other smol_* bindings.
# The binding implements V8 Fast API specializations of Math.* and
# Number.is* — TurboFan inlines them directly into JIT-compiled JS
# callers (~30-50% faster than the uncurryThis-wrapped form on hot
# benchmark loops).
#
# Sequencing: 031 anchors after 027 (smol_util). Insert keeps
# alphabetic order in the smol_* group: smol_power < smol_primordial
# < smol_util < smol_webstreams. (smol_ffi/http/ilp/vfs all come
# before in their respective alphabetic positions.)
#
# Files modified:
# - src/node_binding.cc: register smol_primordial in NODE_BUILTIN_BINDINGS
#
--- a/src/node_binding.cc
+++ b/src/node_binding.cc
@@ -115,6 +115,7 @@
   V(smol_http)                                                                 \
   V(smol_ilp)                                                                  \
   V(smol_power)                                                                \
+  V(smol_primordial)                                                           \
   V(smol_util)                                                                 \
   V(smol_webstreams)
 
